text: Baby(a)lone is a 2015 Luxembourgian Belgian drama movie directed by Donato Rotunno and starring Joshua Defays, Charlotte Elsen, Etienne Halsdorf, Gintare Parulyte, Fabienne Elaine Hollwege. ==Other websites== * * Category:2015 drama movies Category:Belgian drama movies Category:Luxembourgian drama movies Category:Movies directed by Donato Rotunno
title: Baby(a)lone
